```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant P as Producers
  participant K as Kafka (Event Log)
  participant F as Flink Job
  participant L as Iceberg Tables
  participant Q as Trino/BI

  P->>K: publish events
  F->>K: consume events (stream)
  F->>L: write aggregates (streaming upserts/append)
  Q->>L: query current state

  Note over K,F: Logic change or bug fix
  F->>F: deploy new job version
  F->>K: replay from earlier offset / time
  F->>L: recompute and overwrite/merge results
```
